<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Orgo Tech - Crops</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/crop.css">
    <style>
/* General Styles */
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

/* Header */
header {
    background-color: #707e79;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

/* Navbar Styles */
nav {
    background-color: #545f5b;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 25px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(24, 23, 23, 0.5);
}

h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0;
}

/* Navigation Links */
nav ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

nav ul li {
    margin: 0;
}

nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
    background-color: #bbbbbb;
}

/* Logout Button */
#logout-form {
    margin: 0;
}

#logout-button {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

#logout-button:hover {
    background-color: #9a9a9a;
    color: white;
}

/* Main Content */
main {
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: -80px;
    background-color: #b3e0d9;
}

/* Crop Details Section */
#crop-details {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 40px auto;
    width: 80%;
}

.crop-item {
    background-color: #bde0c6;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
    width: 45%;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.crop-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
}

.crop-item h2 {
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: #333;
}

.crop-item p {
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

.crop-item strong {
    color: #333;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px 0;
    margin-top: 40px;
}

button[type="submit"] {
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: none;
    background-color: #ae7bff;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #000000;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

button[type="submit"]:hover {
    background-color: #521bc0;
    color: white;
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        
        <!-- Navigation Links -->
        <nav>
            <h1>Organic Crops</h1>
       
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/home">home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/stores">Stores</a></li>
                <li><a href="/crops">Crops</a></li>
                <li><a href="/achievements">Achievements</a></li>   
            </ul>
            <form action="/logout" method="POST" id="logout-form">
                <button id="logout-button" type="submit">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="crop-details">
            <div class="crop-item">
                <img src="https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/AN313-Tomatoes-732x549-Thumb-732x549.jpg" alt="Crop Image" style=" width: 100%;
                height: 40vh;
                border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;" >
                <h2>Fresh Organic Tomatoes</h2>
                <p>
                    At Orgo Tech, we grow a variety of organic crops that are sourced from different regions across India. One of our best-selling crops is the organic tomato, grown sustainably in fertile soil. These tomatoes are packed with nutrients and offer a delicious, natural flavor.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Region:</strong> Maharashtra <br>
                    <strong>Harvest Season:</strong> Winter <br>
                    <strong>Grown Using:</strong> 100% Organic Farming Techniques
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-item">
                <img src="https://4.imimg.com/data4/AT/RM/MY-29356566/indian-mangoes.jpg" alt="Crop Image" style=" width: 100%;
                height: 40vh;
                border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
                <h2>Sweet Organic Mangoes</h2>
                <p>
                    Our organic mangoes are known for their unparalleled sweetness and quality. Cultivated in the tropical climate of southern India, these mangoes are perfect for juices, desserts, and much more.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Region:</strong> Andhra Pradesh <br>
                    <strong>Harvest Season:</strong> Summer <br>
                    <strong>Grown Using:</strong> No Chemical Pesticides
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Orgo Tech. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
